CustomField.description: Timecard statuses included in the calculation of actual hours for project tasks. If blank, all timecard statuses are included in the calculation.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Add comma-separated timecard statuses to be used in the calculation of actual hours for project tasks. Example: Approved, Submitted. Leave blank to include all timecard statuses in the calculation.
CustomField.label: Timecard Statuses
